 truly the greatest detective in all of Honami!","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006},{"text":"Haha, with so many <ano=Little Namipons><te href=851073>Missing Namipons</te>s</ano> here, this place feels more bustling than ever.","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006},{"text":"Indeed. I love a lively crowd myself as well.","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006},{"text":"There's no need to worry. Every Namipon's a good Namipon. We'd never cause any trouble.","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006},{"text":"Thanks to your help, \"we\" are reunited once again, ready to make Honami City a better place.","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006},{"text":"I look forward to us working together again! Be it chasing urban legends or solving cold cases, you'll always have my full support.","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006},{"text":"Wherever there's a case, there's a detective! The Super Detective Team will always be on the frontline in pursuit of truth.","quest_name":"Namipon Search - The Last Bow","quest_id":165000006}]}